<quantity metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.85" metricValueMax="5.7" metricValueMin="4.0" pageId="20" pageNumber="19" unit="m" value="485.0" valueMax="570.0" valueMin="400.0">400– 570 m</quantity>
) in the rainforest and rain forest-dry forest lowland intergrade in ACG.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
